34fef7af-dfb3-4bba-8522-f0a8d3c1915a.question: How many singers do we have?
34fef7af-dfb3-4bba-8522-f0a8d3c1915a.schema: Table singer: singer_id (INTEGER), name (TEXT), country (TEXT), age (INTEGER)
34fef7af-dfb3-4bba-8522-f0a8d3c1915a.description: Basic COUNT aggregation without WHERE clause

7b1374df-f758-4db5-aa15-6268c70ea901.question: List the name, country and age for all singers ordered by age from the oldest to the youngest.
7b1374df-f758-4db5-aa15-6268c70ea901.sql: SELECT name, country, age FROM singer ORDER BY age DESC
7b1374df-f758-4db5-aa15-6268c70ea901.schema: Table singer: singer_id (INTEGER), name (TEXT), country (TEXT), age (INTEGER)
7b1374df-f758-4db5-aa15-6268c70ea901.description: SELECT multiple columns with ORDER BY DESC

1fae9919-f818-495c-8828-85b7525e20b7.question: What is the average, minimum, and maximum age of all singers from France?
1fae9919-f818-495c-8828-85b7525e20b7.sql: SELECT AVG(age), MIN(age), MAX(age) FROM singer WHERE country = 'France'
1fae9919-f818-495c-8828-85b7525e20b7.schema: Table singer: singer_id (INTEGER), name (TEXT), country (TEXT), age (INTEGER)
1fae9919-f818-495c-8828-85b7525e20b7.keywords: SELECT, AVG, MIN, MAX, FROM, WHERE
1fae9919-f818-495c-8828-85b7525e20b7.description: Multiple aggregations (AVG, MIN, MAX) with WHERE filter

01221598-94a4-425f-8d45-3a3ce4bfa462.question: Show the distinct countries where singers above age 20 are from.
01221598-94a4-425f-8d45-3a3ce4bfa462.sql: SELECT DISTINCT country FROM singer WHERE age > 20
01221598-94a4-425f-8d45-3a3ce4bfa462.schema: Table singer: singer_id (INTEGER), name (TEXT), country (TEXT), age (INTEGER)
01221598-94a4-425f-8d45-3a3ce4bfa462.description: DISTINCT with comparison operator in WHERE

c7558384-ba7a-4302-ab1b-10938d2bd6ff.question: How many singers do we have from each country?
c7558384-ba7a-4302-ab1b-10938d2bd6ff.sql: SELECT country, COUNT(*) FROM singer GROUP BY country
c7558384-ba7a-4302-ab1b-10938d2bd6ff.schema: Table singer: singer_id (INTEGER), name (TEXT), country (TEXT), age (INTEGER)

cda9aead-73a1-4875-a9df-a13497653644.question: Show names of songs whose singer's age is older than the average age.
cda9aead-73a1-4875-a9df-a13497653644.sql: SELECT song_name FROM singer WHERE age > (SELECT AVG(age) FROM singer)
cda9aead-73a1-4875-a9df-a13497653644.schema: Table singer: singer_id (INTEGER), name (TEXT), country (TEXT), age (INTEGER), song_name (TEXT)

f4afaa3b-17cc-40eb-8703-91b8f0347f16.question: Show the stadium name and the number of concerts in each stadium.
f4afaa3b-17cc-40eb-8703-91b8f0347f16.sql: SELECT T2.name, COUNT(*) FROM concert AS T1 JOIN stadium AS T2 ON T1.stadium_id = T2.stadium_id GROUP BY T1.stadium_id
f4afaa3b-17cc-40eb-8703-91b8f0347f16.schema:
Table concert: concert_id (INTEGER), concert_name (TEXT), stadium_id (INTEGER)
Table stadium: stadium_id (INTEGER), name (TEXT), capacity (INTEGER)
f4afaa3b-17cc-40eb-8703-91b8f0347f16.keywords: SELECT, COUNT, FROM, JOIN, ON, GROUP BY
f4afaa3b-17cc-40eb-8703-91b8f0347f16.description: JOIN with GROUP BY and COUNT

aff4d15c-c754-4442-a8f9-db84df3e13ac.question: Show the location and name of stadiums which have some concerts with capacity between 5000 and 10000.
aff4d15c-c754-4442-a8f9-db84df3e13ac.sql: SELECT location, name FROM stadium WHERE capacity BETWEEN 5000 AND 10000
aff4d15c-c754-4442-a8f9-db84df3e13ac.schema: Table stadium: stadium_id (INTEGER), location (TEXT), name (TEXT), capacity (INTEGER)

cf436bae-25ad-421e-956a-9a2c3db30b1f.question: Show the stadium names without any concert.
cf436bae-25ad-421e-956a-9a2c3db30b1f.sql: SELECT name FROM stadium WHERE stadium_id NOT IN (SELECT stadium_id FROM concert)
cf436bae-25ad-421e-956a-9a2c3db30b1f.schema:
Table stadium: stadium_id (INTEGER), name (TEXT)
Table concert: concert_id (INTEGER), stadium_id (INTEGER)
cf436bae-25ad-421e-956a-9a2c3db30b1f.keywords: SELECT, FROM, WHERE, NOT IN, SUBQUERY
cf436bae-25ad-421e-956a-9a2c3db30b1f.description: NOT IN with subquery for exclusion

b0d1082f-72ea-41c8-b954-32418ee46e70.question: What are the countries that have both singers above age 40 and singers below age 30?
b0d1082f-72ea-41c8-b954-32418ee46e70.sql: SELECT country FROM singer WHERE age > 40 INTERSECT SELECT country FROM singer WHERE age < 30
b0d1082f-72ea-41c8-b954-32418ee46e70.schema: Table singer: singer_id (INTEGER), name (TEXT), country (TEXT), age (INTEGER)
b0d1082f-72ea-41c8-b954-32418ee46e70.description: INTERSECT for finding items matching BOTH conditions

e9566b4d-3f12-4dce-9b25-14a309565ade.question: Show all birth years of singers from France or singers from USA.
e9566b4d-3f12-4dce-9b25-14a309565ade.sql: SELECT birth_year FROM singer WHERE country = 'France' UNION SELECT birth_year FROM singer WHERE country = 'USA'
e9566b4d-3f12-4dce-9b25-14a309565ade.schema: Table singer: singer_id (INTEGER), name (TEXT), country (TEXT), birth_year (INTEGER)
e9566b4d-3f12-4dce-9b25-14a309565ade.description: UNION for combining results from multiple conditions

1cb38f0b-1db5-47cb-92d9-3a2bcae24d4d.question: Find names of stadiums that did not have a concert in 2014.
1cb38f0b-1db5-47cb-92d9-3a2bcae24d4d.sql: SELECT name FROM stadium EXCEPT SELECT T2.name FROM concert AS T1 JOIN stadium AS T2 ON T1.stadium_id = T2.stadium_id WHERE T1.year = 2014
1cb38f0b-1db5-47cb-92d9-3a2bcae24d4d.schema:
Table stadium: stadium_id (INTEGER), name (TEXT)
Table concert: concert_id (INTEGER), stadium_id (INTEGER), year (INTEGER)

27afd589-1cb8-4128-87fe-bca75eb66bb9.question: List all singers whose song name contains 'Hey'.
27afd589-1cb8-4128-87fe-bca75eb66bb9.sql: SELECT name FROM singer WHERE song_name LIKE '%Hey%'
27afd589-1cb8-4128-87fe-bca75eb66bb9.description: LIKE with wildcards for pattern matching

8412dae7-29ef-43e6-89b1-657f821479c8.question: Find the first name and gender of students who have more than one pet.
8412dae7-29ef-43e6-89b1-657f821479c8.sql: SELECT T1.fname, T1.sex FROM student AS T1 JOIN has_pet AS T2 ON T1.stuid = T2.stuid GROUP BY T1.stuid HAVING COUNT(*) > 1
8412dae7-29ef-43e6-89b1-657f821479c8.schema:
Table student: stuid (INTEGER), fname (TEXT), sex (TEXT)
Table has_pet: stuid (INTEGER), petid (INTEGER)
8412dae7-29ef-43e6-89b1-657f821479c8.keywords: SELECT, FROM, JOIN, GROUP BY, HAVING
8412dae7-29ef-43e6-89b1-657f821479c8.description: HAVING clause for filtering grouped results

03d93463-e6ee-4c8d-b60d-4af6ca655ae0.question: Show names of singers who performed in concerts in 2014.
03d93463-e6ee-4c8d-b60d-4af6ca655ae0.sql: SELECT T2.name FROM singer_in_concert AS T1 JOIN singer AS T2 ON T1.singer_id = T2.singer_id JOIN concert AS T3 ON T1.concert_id = T3.concert_id WHERE T3.year = 2014
03d93463-e6ee-4c8d-b60d-4af6ca655ae0.schema:
Table singer: singer_id (INTEGER), name (TEXT)
Table singer_in_concert: singer_id (INTEGER), concert_id (INTEGER)
Table concert: concert_id (INTEGER), concert_name (TEXT), year (INTEGER)

20e98be8-df83-422a-8fb9-f9628be59dca.question: Show the stadium name and capacity with highest average attendance.
20e98be8-df83-422a-8fb9-f9628be59dca.sql: SELECT name, capacity FROM stadium ORDER BY average DESC LIMIT 1
20e98be8-df83-422a-8fb9-f9628be59dca.schema: Table stadium: stadium_id (INTEGER), name (TEXT), capacity (INTEGER), average (REAL)
20e98be8-df83-422a-8fb9-f9628be59dca.keywords: SELECT, FROM, ORDER BY, DESC, LIMIT
20e98be8-df83-422a-8fb9-f9628be59dca.description: ORDER BY with LIMIT to find maximum

bc3c2131-7e9d-4c79-8490-31433de4b3bf.question: How many concerts are there in 2014 or 2015?
bc3c2131-7e9d-4c79-8490-31433de4b3bf.sql: SELECT COUNT(*) FROM concert WHERE year = 2014 OR year = 2015

30be6617-f740-4083-976d-4ea315dc8952.question: Show stadium name and capacity for the stadium with most concerts after 2013, and sort by the number of concerts in descending order.
30be6617-f740-4083-976d-4ea315dc8952.sql: SELECT T2.name, T2.capacity FROM concert AS T1 JOIN stadium AS T2 ON T1.stadium_id = T2.stadium_id WHERE T1.year > 2013 GROUP BY T2.stadium_id ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC LIMIT 1
30be6617-f740-4083-976d-4ea315dc8952.schema:
Table concert: concert_id (INTEGER), stadium_id (INTEGER), year (INTEGER)
Table stadium: stadium_id (INTEGER), name (TEXT), capacity (INTEGER)
30be6617-f740-4083-976d-4ea315dc8952.keywords: SELECT, FROM, JOIN, WHERE, GROUP BY, ORDER BY, LIMIT
30be6617-f740-4083-976d-4ea315dc8952.description: Complex query with JOIN, WHERE, GROUP BY, ORDER BY, LIMIT

2b738e02-ba60-4bd7-95c2-940f83aa5e53.question: How many concerts occurred in the stadium with the largest capacity?
2b738e02-ba60-4bd7-95c2-940f83aa5e53.sql: SELECT COUNT(*) FROM concert WHERE stadium_id = (SELECT stadium_id FROM stadium ORDER BY capacity DESC LIMIT 1)
2b738e02-ba60-4bd7-95c2-940f83aa5e53.schema:
Table concert: concert_id (INTEGER), stadium_id (INTEGER)
Table stadium: stadium_id (INTEGER), capacity (INTEGER)
2b738e02-ba60-4bd7-95c2-940f83aa5e53.keywords: SELECT, COUNT, FROM, WHERE, SUBQUERY, ORDER BY, LIMIT
2b738e02-ba60-4bd7-95c2-940f83aa5e53.description: Nested subquery with ORDER BY and LIMIT

5d2d4c3e-59ec-4f24-80b2-0cc864136a00.question: Find the maximum and minimum weight for each pet type.
5d2d4c3e-59ec-4f24-80b2-0cc864136a00.sql: SELECT MAX(weight), pettype FROM pets GROUP BY pettype
